#Text=Wikinews interviews Spanish Paralympic track and field athlete Elena Congost Mohedano
#Text=Thursday , July 18 , 2013
#Text=Laura
#Text=Hale
#Text=interviews Elena Congost Mohedano for Wikinews
#Text=Elena Congost Mohedano at the airport in Madrid before departing for France Image : Laura Hale .

#Text=With the IPC Athletics World Championships scheduled to start this Friday , Wikinews interviewed Spanish T12 classified long distance runner Elena Congost Mohedano at Madrid – Barajas Airport Monday before he departed for Lyon , France .
#Text=Congost is scheduled to compete in the T12 1500 meters .

#Text=( ( Wikinews ) ) Hello , I 'm interviewing Elena Congost Mohedano who is a Spanish Paralympic athlete who won a silver in London and is going to Lyon to compete in the 2013 IPC Athletics World Championships .
#Text=Having won a medal in London are you going to get another one in this one ?
#Text=Elena Congost Mohedano : Yes ! I train all year to go to win a medal .
#Text=( ( WN ) ) Which medal ?
#Text=Elena Congost Mohedano : Gold ! ( laughs )
#Text=( ( WN ) ) Which event ?
#Text=Elena Congost Mohedano : In 1500m .
#Text=( ( WN ) )
#Text=So you 're a long distance runner .
#Text=And you do n't train/run with a guide because you 're , what , T-13 ?
#Text=Elena Congost Mohedano : I 'm T-12 .
#Text=( ( WN ) ) Ah .
#Text=So you have a degenerative eye disease , so your vision is getting worse ? ( ( es))Spanish language : ‍¿Tu visión empeora ?
#Text=Elena Congost Mohedano : Yes .
#Text=( ( WN ) ) Do you expect it to get much worse over your continued history competing ?
#Text=Elena Congost Mohedano : Now it 's stalled , but next year it 's possible .
#Text=( ( WN ) ) Do you plan to stick since you 've been competing since 2002 , right ... ?
#Text=Elena Congost Mohedano : Yes , [ Unintelligible ] .
#Text=( ( WN ) ) Do you plan to continue running until 2020 if Madrid gets the Games ?
#Text=Elena Congost Mohedano :
#Text=I do n't know . ( laughs ) First 2016 in Rio , and then ...
#Text=I do n't know .
#Text=( ( WN ) ) There 's so few women competing for Spain .
#Text=Is that an additional challenge as an athlete in this country ?
#Text=Elena Congost Mohedano : No ...
#Text=In this country there are more girls in 100m , 200m and long jump .
#Text=More people .
#Text=In middle distance no .
#Text=Two , three , four girls only .
#Text=( ( WN ) ) Why do you think there 's so few women on the Spanish team ?
#Text=It 's like 27 total Spanish competing , and there 's like [ three ] women ?
#Text=Elena Congost Mohedano : I do n't know ...
#Text=The level is high internationally , but in Spain ... no more level .
#Text=( ( WN ) ) Someone with a visual impairement , there 's a lot of sports you could do ?
#Text=Elena Congost Mohedano :
#Text=The people now are very lazy . ( laughs ) No one runs . ( laughs )
#Text=( ( WN ) ) With so many sporting opportunities for people with vision impairments in Spain , why did you choose track and field ?
#Text=Elena Congost Mohedano : When I was young , my dream was to become an athlete .
#Text=I saw them in tv , in races , and I told my parents " my wish is to win a gold medal in the Olympics ! "
#Text=( ( WN ) ) Is there any particular athlete you remember from when you were young being particularly inspiring ?
#Text=Elena Congost Mohedano : No.
#Text=( ( WN ) ) Spain has these really distinctive uniforms .
#Text=The colors ...
#Text=Do people ever comment to you about them ?
#Text=Because in the US they were like , " your uniforms look like McDonald 's ! " ( ( es))Spanish language :
#Text=‍¿Hay alguien que ha dicho algo de lo que es el color y tal , porque por lo visto en EE . UU dicen que son como McDonalds .
#Text=Elena Congost Mohedano : ( laughs ) In London , everyone said they were not good ...
#Text=They said we looked like clowns .
#Text=But this one now is ... redder .
#Text=Better .
#Text=( ( WN ) ) As somebody who 's been competing for more than ten years , has there been a big change in the Paralympic movement from your perspective ?
#Text=Elena Congost Mohedano : Yes !
#Text=Every year the level is higher .
#Text=In the Paralympics , every four years I increase my performance level .
#Text=( ( WN ) ) Do you think that the increased competition has made you a better athlete ?
#Text=Elena Congost Mohedano : Yes ! Yes .
#Text=( ( WN ) ) Thank you very much !
#Text=Elena Congost Mohedano : Okay !
